<subSubSection pageId="211" pageNumber="490" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6707690" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6707690" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6707690/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="211" pageNumber="490" targetBox="[115,705,3062,3477]" targetPageId="211">
<paragraph blockId="211.[728,1321,3055,3478]" pageId="211" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[729,905,3252,3281]" pageId="211" pageNumber="490">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known only from three localities in E Brazil (Minas Gerais and Espiritu Santo states).
</paragraph>
</caption>
